title: "AMR Sentinel: an open-source antimicrobial resistance surveillance and clinical stewardship platform"
message: "If you use AMR Sentinel in academic work, please cite it using the metadata in this file."
type: software
authors:
  - given-names: Tejashwar Reddy
    family-names: Katika
    email: TejashwarReddyKatika@my.unt.edu
    affiliation: "Independent Researcher (affiliated with the University of North Texas)"
    orcid: "https://orcid.org/0009-0006-3015-5697"
  - given-names: Akhilesh Reddy
